  "system": {
    "biography": "<p>A fire-immune Awakened scorpion (Euscorpius igneus) often conditioned as a security animal; it strikes with claws and a venomous sting.</p><p><strong>Powers:</strong> Immunity to Fire, Venom</p><p><em>Attacks: 4L claws + 5S stinger, Reach −1. Habitat: Wide range (prefers rocks, stones, brick walls, buildings). Range: Southern Europe; occasional in northern European port towns and cities. Two attacks on one target per Complex Action (claws 4L + stinger 5S). In a toxic domain the stinger is 7S or 4D. A claw hit lets it grab (victim Quickness (4) Test); while held it bites with claw + stinger, raising those to 5L / 6S. Book Body 2/1, Intelligence 1/4. PAE p.91.</em></p>",
